{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01C6MaumwaQ69B9AAEEb7wxb","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_019ygPCMjPZbj8r3ubpVpR8i","name":"Bash","input":{"command":"git add scripts/tests/test_set_version.sh dev/plans/runs/0.6.1-AXIS-E-PIN-output.json && git commit -m \"test(set-version): add axis-E pin regression sentinel (test #13)\n\nAdds test case 13 to scripts/tests/test_set_version.sh. Simulates\n--workspace 0.6.1 when BOTH axes start at 0.6.0, asserting:\n\n  (a) workspace version flips to 0.6.1\n  (b) fathomdb-embedder-api/Cargo.toml [package].version stays 0.6.0\n  (c) workspace.dependencies pin for fathomdb-embedder-api stays 0.6.0\n  (d) every non-embedder-api crate retains version.workspace = true\n  (e) --check-files exits 0 after the bump\n\nRegression novelty: prior tests 2 and 12 cannot catch silent axis-E\nmutation in the same-starting-version scenario. Test 13 explicitly\nchecks the retained 0.6.0 value so a future set_workspace_dep_axis_w_versions()\nedit that drops the embedder-api guard is immediately caught.\n\nScript is UNCHANGED — all 23 tests GREEN on first run.\nWired into CI via agent-test.sh (run_capped test-set-version).\n\nCloses slice 0.6.1-AXIS-E-PIN.\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>\"","description":"Commit the new regression test and output JSON"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":669,"cache_read_input_tokens":33826,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":669},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"4851922d-2a7d-4929-9e12-caa05c2d927b","uuid":"7b6a589d-81f9-4f76-b60e-e6943d90c80e","request_id":"req_011CbN4D6Ves8u82Sjprhtxo"}
